    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "あれからいろいろ試したが……どうにも……\n沙季。やっぱり一度、監督に掛け合うのも手かもな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "あれからいろいろ試したが……どうにも……\n沙季。やっぱり一度、監督に掛け合うのも手かもな",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.6054418882
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_03-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "ま、待って下さい！！　{user}さん！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "ま、待って下さい！！　{user}さん！！",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.6054418882,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-03.m4a",
          "delay": 5194.558111800001,
          "startTime": 14.8
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.0000001271
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "すまない。もう時間もないし――って、うわあっ！？\nび、びしょびしょだ……なんだ、何が起きた？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "すまない。もう時間もないし――って、うわあっ！？\nび、びしょびしょだ……なんだ、何が起きた？",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.1666667938,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon",
      "startTime": 22.4083438557
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_03-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "で、ですから待って下さいと……ふふ……っ……\n言ったんです……うふふっ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "で、ですから待って下さいと……ふふ……っ……\n言ったんです……うふふっ……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.5333334605,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.0816770554
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_03-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "すずちゃんが、ふふ……プールに飛び込んだ時の\n水飛沫が飛んできていましたから……ふふふっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "すずちゃんが、ふふ……プールに飛び込んだ時の\n水飛沫が飛んできていましたから……ふふふっ！",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.2000001271,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon",
      "startTime": 34.5706780116
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_03-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "でも、まさかこんなピンポイントで掛かるなんて……！\n前髪もおでこにべったり張り付いてますし、あはは！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "でも、まさかこんなピンポイントで掛かるなんて……！\n前髪もおでこにべったり張り付いてますし、あはは！",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.4992493429,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon",
      "startTime": 42.777344354
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ど、どうしたんだ沙季\nなぜそんなにツボに入っているんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "ど、どうしたんだ沙季\nなぜそんなにツボに入っているんだ？",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.7333334605,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_03-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "す、すみません……ふふ……悪気はないんですが……\nはぁ……なんだか、昔の自分を思い出してしまいました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "す、すみません……ふふ……悪気はないんですが……\nはぁ……なんだか、昔の自分を思い出してしまいました",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.3333334605,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon",
      "startTime": 57.2480459373
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_03-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "ずっと昔、千紗と水族館に行った時のことなんですが\n私達は両親とはぐれて、迷子になってしまったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "ずっと昔、千紗と水族館に行った時のことなんですが\n私達は両親とはぐれて、迷子になってしまったんです",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.8999996185,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_03-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "不安で泣く千紗を見たら、どうにかして励ましたい\n笑顔にしたい、って思いまして",
      "translations": {
        "en": "不安で泣く千紗を見たら、どうにかして励ましたい\n笑顔にしたい、って思いまして",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.2333329518,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon",
      "startTime": 72.694394986
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、確かいきなり、水を被ったんだろう？\n前に、千紗から聞いたことがあるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "あぁ、確かいきなり、水を被ったんだろう？\n前に、千紗から聞いたことがあるよ",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.7666662852,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "しかも、それでも千紗が泣き止まなかったから\n水槽に飛び込もうとしていたらしいな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "しかも、それでも千紗が泣き止まなかったから\n水槽に飛び込もうとしていたらしいな",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_03-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "はい。その時の自分と、{user}さんが\n重なって見えたのもあって、なんだかおかしくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "はい。その時の自分と、{user}さんが\n重なって見えたのもあって、なんだかおかしくて",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.9872988043,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon",
      "startTime": 93.7816514811
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_03-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "あ……もしかして、水鉄砲を急に撃ってきたり\n浮き輪遊びを始めたのは、私を励まそうと……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "あ……もしかして、水鉄砲を急に撃ってきたり\n浮き輪遊びを始めたのは、私を励まそうと……？",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.6333329518,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.7356176538
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "い、一応そのつもりだった……\n失敗に終わったが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "い、一応そのつもりだった……\n失敗に終わったが……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.4666662852,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon",
      "startTime": 107.3807195507
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_03-ski010.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、不器用過ぎますよ……ふふふっ！\nダメ、またツボに入って……あははっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "ふふっ、不器用過ぎますよ……ふふふっ！\nダメ、またツボに入って……あははっ！",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.5666662852,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon",
      "startTime": 116.0977035049
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_03-ski011.m4a",
      "text": "はー……沢山笑ったらなんだか気持ちが楽になりました\nありがとうございます、{user}さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "はー……沢山笑ったらなんだか気持ちが楽になりました\nありがとうございます、{user}さん",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.6999996185,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "正直、想定外だったんだが……そうだな\n沙季の今の笑顔は、自然で、とっても輝いて見えるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "正直、想定外だったんだが……そうだな\n沙季の今の笑顔は、自然で、とっても輝いて見えるよ",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.9999996185,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon",
      "startTime": 133.4711275899
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_03-ski012.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そう言われると照れてしまうんですが……\n私、難しく考え過ぎていたのかもしれませんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "そ、そう言われると照れてしまうんですが……\n私、難しく考え過ぎていたのかもしれませんね",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.0999996185,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_03-ski013.m4a",
      "text": "頭で考えるよりも、大事なのは心。そして、誰かを\n笑顔にしたい、という想いだったのかもしれません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "頭で考えるよりも、大事なのは心。そして、誰かを\n笑顔にしたい、という想いだったのかもしれません",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.099993515,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon",
      "startTime": 151.558377632
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_03-ski014.m4a",
      "text": "今なら、きっと……監督が求める曲のイメージを\n私なりに、明るくはしゃいで表現出来る気がします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "今なら、きっと……監督が求める曲のイメージを\n私なりに、明るくはしゃいで表現出来る気がします",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.0666662852,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon",
      "startTime": 160.262753662
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_03-ski015.m4a",
      "text": "それに、今年の夏、ミクさんと行う撮影は\nこの一度きりです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "それに、今年の夏、ミクさんと行う撮影は\nこの一度きりです",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
